<p>
  <span class="nym">Tobias</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Greek</span> <i>Τοβίας</i> from <span class="lang">Hebrew</span> <i>טוביה</i> 'the goodness of God'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The titular character in the apocryphal Book of Tobit. Wycliffite Bible (1395): <i>Thobie</i>, <i>Tobie</i>.</p>
</div>
  
  


